{"sn36.1:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 36.1 ","sn36.1:0.2":"1. Sagathavagga ","sn36.1:0.3":"Samadhisutta ","sn36.1:1.1":"“Tisso ima, bhikkhave, vedana. ","sn36.1:1.2":"Katama tisso? ","sn36.1:1.3":"Sukha vedana, dukkha vedana, adukkhamasukha vedana—","sn36.1:1.4":"ima kho, bhikkhave, tisso vedanati. ","sn36.1:2.1":"Samahito sampajano, ","sn36.1:2.2":"sato buddhassa savako; ","sn36.1:2.3":"Vedana ca pajanati, ","sn36.1:2.4":"vedanananca sambhavam. ","sn36.1:3.1":"Yattha ceta nirujjhanti, ","sn36.1:3.2":"magganca khayagaminam; ","sn36.1:3.3":"Vedananam khaya bhikkhu, ","sn36.1:3.4":"nicchato parinibbuto”ti. ","sn36.1:3.5":"Pathamam. "}